3312.Name: MAPTA Women's  "Chaos In A Cage" PTI Open
3312.Details:
Welcome to the 2021 Women's Chaos In A Cage Tourney! This is a Women's Open PTI tournament taking place Saturday November 6th.
32 team draw played in one day! Matches will start at 8am at Aronimink & Waynesborough.  
Check in/Pickup Favor/Continental Breakfast @ Overbrook Golf Club between 7am-9am
Format:
All main draw and consolation matches will play 2 out of 3 sets using regular scoring. Tiebreaker at 6-6. 
Prizes: Winners and finalists of main draw win prizes. Only Champions of consolation brackets will win prizes.

TO REGISTER: PLEASE CLICK ON THE "REGISTER" TAB ABOVE
3312.RegistrationDetails:
Registration: Check in and pick up your favor at Overbrook between 7am-9am.
Amenities: Continental breakfast, lunch, early dinner , favor, and tons of paddle!  Cost is $180/team  
Start times will be emailed on Friday November 5th by 3pm
